OL,3,CBlackpool South by-election: All you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FVoters will go to the polls in the
OL,7,FBlackpool South by-election on 2 May.
OL,9,FIt was triggered by the resignation of
OL,10,FConservative former MP Scott Benton,
OL,11,Fwho was suspended for 35 days after
OL,12,Fbecoming embroiled in a lobbying
OL,13,Fscandal.
OL,15,FIt falls on the same day as local
OL,16,Felections across England and Wales,
OL,17,Fbut voters who live in the
OL,18,Fconstituency are unaffected.
OL,20,FPolls will open at 7am and close at
OL,21,F10pm.
