OL,3,CBlackpool South by-election: All you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FWhat is the constituency like?
OL,8,FBlackpool South comprises of the
OL,9,Fcentral and southern parts of
OL,10,FBlackpool, including Blackpool Tower
OL,11,Fand the Pleasure Beach.
OL,13,FBlackpool FC and the site of Blackpool
OL,14,FAirport are also within the boundaries.
OL,16,FThe constituency was held by the
OL,17,FConservatives for more than 50 years
OL,18,Funtil Labour's historic country-wide
OL,19,Flandslide in 1997.
