OL,3,CBlackpool South by-election: All you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FIt then formed a tower of strength in
OL,7,Fthe so-called red wall, until it
OL,8,Ftoppled to the Conservatives once
OL,9,Fagain in 2019.
OL,11,FNow the marginal seat - with a
OL,12,FConservative majority of 3,690 - is
OL,13,Fbeing targeted by Labour once again.
OL,15,FWhat happened to trigger the by-
OL,16,Felection?
OL,18,FMr Benton was caught by the Times in
OL,19,FApril 2023 offering to lobby ministers
OL,20,Fand table parliamentary questions on
OL,21,Fbehalf of gambling investors.
