OL,3,CBlackpool South by-election: All you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FThe undercover showed the former MP
OL,7,Fexplaining how he could use his
OL,8,Fposition to try and limit the biggest
OL,9,Freforms to gambling laws since 2005.
OL,11,FAfter it was referred to the Commons
OL,12,FStandards Committee, Mr Benton's
OL,13,Factions were found to be an "extremely
OL,14,Fserious breach" of the rules.
OL,16,FIt recommended a 35 day suspension,
OL,17,Fwhich was backed by the House of
OL,18,FCommons, and as it began the process
OL,19,Fof triggering a by-election.
