OL,6,FBut a month later, Mr Benton announced
OL,7,Fon social media .
OL,9,FWho are the candidates?
OL,11,FThere are nine candidates running in
OL,12,Fthe by-election.
OL,14,FOn his Tik Tok profile, Stephen Black
OL,15,Fsays "vote for yourselves" calling for
OL,16,F"bringing utilities back into public
OL,17,Fownership" and a "sustainable economy".
