OL,3,CBlackpool South by-election: All you
OL,4,Cneed to know
OL,6,FMark Butcher says he can provide
OL,7,F"loyalty" and "dedication" to the
OL,8,Fpeople of Blackpool and he wants to
OL,9,F"set a new standard for anyone who is
OL,10,Fdealing with the homeless or
OL,11,Fvulnerable people"
OL,13,FAndrew Cregan says he wants to "fight
OL,14,Fto make Blackpool a great place to
OL,15,Flive, move to and invest in."
OL,17,FHowling Laud Hope's plans include
OL,18,F"selling Blackpool to Walt Disney" and
OL,19,F"rejuvenating" the town's airport.
