OL,6,FOn their campaign website, Damon Sharp
OL,7,Fsays he wants to "document how bad
OL,8,Fthings are" and "create a preferred
OL,9,Ffuture state" with a "plan how to get
OL,10,Fthere".
OL,12,FHe says it will be "published for
OL,13,Fpublic comment so we can all decide
OL,14,Fwhat needs to be done to fix Blackpool
OL,15,FSouth".
OL,17,FBen Thomas "believes that Green
OL,18,Fpolicies can help make Blackpool great
OL,19,Fagain" and has plans to "beat the
OL,20,Fhousing crisis, the climate emergency
OL,21,Fand the high cost of living".
